    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Qualifier used for attributions of works by an unknown architect or other creator working for a named architect or other creator in the 18th century through the present, when the group of people working for the architect calls itself an office (e.g., office of ChristopherWren).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
